        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"thumbs up\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f44d\" role=\"img\" title=\"thumbs up\">:thumbs_up:</span> pchickey submitted <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13366#pullrequestreview-4291372920\">PR review</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Thanks. This would be a nice optimization to apply to wasmtime-wasi-io by default, in a follow up PR. As of now, it gets no CI testing, idk if we should add something for it in this PR or just count on it being tested via wasmtime-wasi-io in a follow up?</p>\n</blockquote>",
